  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.kuka.motion.IMotion, IAction, ISunriseMotion, ISunriseMotionExtended
    Deprecated. 
    To avoid several bugs with motion batches, it is recommended to use single motions instead.

    @Deprecated
public class MotionBatch
extends RobotMotion<MotionBatch>
    Represents a list of motions that are executed one after another within a single motion sequence.
